{
  "name": "Frostbite",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You cause numbing frost to form on one creature that you can see within range. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, the target takes [[/r 1d6]] cold damage, and it has disadvantage on the next weapon attack roll it makes before the end of its next turn.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The spell's damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] when you reach 5th level ([[/r 2d6]]), 11th level ([[/r 3d6]]), and 17th level ([[/r 4d6]]).</p></div>",
